reviewText: Sing Karaoke without leaving the comfort of your home!! This is a great set, and is expandable with any other DVD Karaoke Discs. Great Collection of 17 songs to give you a taste of the fun you could have with karaoke at home!! Over The Rainbow, New York New York, Tomorrow, Dancing Queen, I Will Survive, You Can't Hurry Love, and more classic tracks. Excellent sound quality and backing vocals as well!
